  "instructions": [
    "Preheat smoker or smoker-safe oven to 225°F (107°C).",
    "Slice sweet potatoes into 1/2-inch cubes and place in a baking sheet.",
    "Drizzle with 1 tbsp maple syrup and 1/4 tsp smoked paprika; toss to coat.",
    "Smoke at low heat for 20-25 minutes or until tender and slightly caramelized.",
    "Let cool slightly, then serve with a sprinkle of sea salt for balance."
